<h2 id="remote-repository-github">Remote repository (Github)</h2>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>two methods : https / ssh</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Approaches:</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<ul>
  <li>(1) add to stage
    <blockquote>
      <p>git add filename</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
  <li>(2) add to local repository
    <blockquote>
      <p>git commit -m ‚ÄúComment‚Äù</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
  <li>(3) push to remote repository
    <blockquote>
      <p>git push</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
  <li>(4) pull the latest code version
    <blockquote>
      <p>git pull</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
</ul>

<ol>
  <li>branch (crud)</li>
</ol>

<blockquote>
  <ul>
    <li>git branch branchname</li>
    <li>git branch -d branchname</li>
    <li>git merge branchname</li>
    <li>git branch</li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>

<ol>
  <li>Conflict</li>
</ol>

<blockquote>
  <ul>
    <li>git pull</li>
    <li>talk about the diff and figure out the result</li>
    <li>then git add / git commit the result</li>
    <li>finally git merge  / git push  ~~</li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>
